  <summary date="2017-07-17T04:00:00Z" status="Introduced in House">Federal Employee Pension Fairness Act of 2017

This bill repeals provisions requiring federal employees, including foreign service employees,&#160;who began service after 2012&#160;to pay an increased contribution (4.4%,&#160;up from 0.8%)&#160;toward funding their annuities under the Federal Employees Retirement System.</summary>
